{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":false,"flaws":{},"title":"submit","mdn_url":"/de/docs/Web/API/HTMLFormElement/submit_event","locale":"de","native":"Deutsch","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>Das <code>submit</code> Event tritt ein, wenn ein Formular (<code>&lt;form ...&gt;&lt;/form&gt;</code>) abgeschickt wird.</p>\n\n<p>Es gilt zu beachten, dass das <code>submit</code> Event <strong>nur</strong> auf dem Formularelement ausgelöst wird. Der auslösende <code>&lt;button&gt;</code> oder <code>&lt;input type=\"submit\" ... /&gt;</code> erhalten das Event nicht (Es wird das Formular abgeschickt, nicht der Button).</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"allgemein","title":"Allgemein","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>Spezifikation</strong></td>\n   <td><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.whatwg.org/specs/web-apps/current-work/multipage/association-of-controls-and-forms.html#form-submission-algorithm\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>Interface</strong></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>Propagiert (\"Bubbles\")</strong></td>\n   <td>Ja (obwohl eigentlich einfach Event ohne Propagation)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>Cancelable</strong></td>\n   <td>Ja</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>Ziel</strong></td>\n   <td>Element</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><strong>Standardaktion</strong></td>\n   <td>Abhängig von Implementierung (schickt Inhalt des Formulars zum Server)</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"eigenschaften","title":"Eigenschaften","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Property</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Type</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">Description</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></td>\n   <td>The event target (the topmost target in the DOM tree).</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>The type of event.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event normally bubbles or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"Dieser Wert kann nicht verändert werden.\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">Schreibgeschützt </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/de/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>Whether the event is cancellable or not.</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Allgemein","id":"allgemein"},{"text":"Eigenschaften","id":"eigenschaften"}],"summary":"Das submit Event tritt ein, wenn ein Formular (<form ...></form>) abgeschickt wird.","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"HTMLFormElement: submit event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onsubmit","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"submit","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"HTMLFormElement: submit イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"GlobalEventHandlers.onsubmit","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"titl